      "timestampEdited": null,
      "callEndedTimestamp": null,
      "isPinned": false,
      "content": "Unfortunately, OpenROAD does not currently differentiate between data and hold buffers during buffer selection: https://github.com/The-OpenROAD-Project/OpenROAD/issues/10622\n\nWhile you can disable all delay buffers, this would also mean that they could not be used for hold repair.",
